item.title: fatal: unable to access ‘https://github.com/Homebrew/brew/‘: Error in the HTTP2 framing layer
item.description: 问题描述 解决：fatal: unable to access ‘https://github.com/Homebrew/brew/’: Error in the HTTP2 framing layer fatal: unable to access 'https://github.com/homebrew/brew/': 1 更新了新的系统，安装homebrew的时候老失败。 解决方案： git config --global --unset http.proxy git
